lbum-brazil-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-weeknd-new-album-brazil-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weeknd">The Weeknd</a>公布了他即将发行的专辑《明天快点》的艺术作品。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463">《The Weeknd》——“黎明 FM”评论：深情的明星带着希望和后见之明迎接新的一天</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位艺术家的真名是 Abel Tesfaye，自一月份起就一直在预告新音乐，当时他在一系列社交媒体帖子中表示，他正在进行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-after-hours-review-his-most-all-encompassing-record-to-date-is-also-an-existential-quandary-2632591">“After Hours”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463">“Dawn FM”</a>三部曲的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-teases-return-with-after-hours-and-dawn-fm-sequel-3567220">第三章即将</a>推出。</p><p>此后，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-shares-snippet-of-new-music-in-cinematic-teaser-3777326">全年分享了新曲目的片段</a>，并最终<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-unveils-details-of-new-album-hurry-up-tomorrow-3790669">在本周早些时候透露了专辑名称“Hurry Up Tomorrow”</a> 。</p><p>现在，这位“拯救你的眼泪”歌手在社交媒体上公布了这件艺术品。它有一个简单的脸部特写镜头，与他“下班后”时代所见的面部假肢不同。发布日期尚未确定。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_oJ_l0OSke/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" backg