以下是 The Weeknd 在他的圣保罗特别音乐会上演奏的内容https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-the-weeknd-played-at-his-special-sao-paulo-concert-3791657?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=heres-what-the-周末在他的圣保罗特别音乐会上演奏Laura MolloySun, 08 Sep 2024 08:22:49 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music NewsPophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3791657 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年 9 月 7 日，“The Weeknd”Abel Tesfaye 在巴西圣保罗 MorumBIS 举办的“After Hours Til Dawn Tour”中登台表演。图片来源：Wagner Meier/Getty Images for Live Nation" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> The Weeknd 在音乐会上首次亮相了他即将发行的专辑《Hurry Up Tomorrow》中的八首新歌</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-the-weeknd-played-at-his-special-sao-paulo-concert-3791657">《这是 The Weeknd 在他的圣保罗特别音乐会上演奏的内容》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年 9 月 7 日，“The Weeknd”Abel Tesfaye 在巴西圣保罗 MorumBIS 举办的“After Hours Til Dawn Tour”中登台表演。图片来源：Wagner Meier/Getty Images for Live Nation" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weeknd">The Weeknd</a>昨晚在圣保罗举办了一场“仅限一晚”的现场直播音乐会。在下面查看他演奏的所有内容。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463">《The Weeknd》——“黎明 FM”评论：深情的明星带着希望和后见之明迎接新的一天</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-to-play-one-night-only-show-in-brazil-with-never-before-seen-production-3775945">一次性演出</a>是在9月7日星期六在圣保罗的EstádioMorumbis地点举行的。这是歌手 - 真实姓名Abel Tesfaye  - 在过去的两年中开始了他的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-breaks-london-stadium-attendance-record-on-after-hours-til-dawn-tour-3469047" target="_blank" rel="noopener">小时黎明之旅</a>”，并标记了音乐新时代的开始。</p><p>在演出之前，这位歌手透露，这与他的上一阶段的演出有所不同， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-to-play-one-night-only-show-in-brazil-with-never-before-seen-production-3775945">其中包括混合列表和“从未见过的作品”</a> 。特斯法伊还与联合国世界粮食计划计划联合起来，从出售给<a href="https://www.wfp.org/theweeknd" target="_blank" rel="noopener">XO人道主义基金</a>的每张门票中捐赠了1美元（77便士），以结束全球饥饿危机。</p><p>竞技场的观众大约有75,000人，数以百万计的观众进入了直播，这位巨大的演出使《周末》赛车席卷了他最大的热门歌曲，同时还从他即将发行的专辑“ Purrine Up明天”中亮相了八首新歌。</p><p>这是艺术家戏弄新音乐的几个月之后，从他建议即将到来的他正在进行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-after-hours-review-his-most-all-encompassing-record-to-date-is-also-an-existential-quandary-2632591">“小时后”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463">“黎明FM”的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-teases-return-with-after-hours-and-dawn-fm-sequel-3567220">第三章</a>即将在一月份的一系列社交媒体帖子中。此后，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-shares-snippet-of-new-music-in-cinematic-teaser-3777326">在本年度分享了新曲目的片段</a>，并终于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-unveils-details-of-new-album-hurry-up-tomorrow-3790669">在本周早些时候透露了专辑标题“ Purrin Up Tomorrow”</a> 。</p><p>在新时代，《招手》在演出开始时首次亮相了两首新曲目。尽管他没有透露歌曲唱片，但在线粉丝们还是创造了他们“淡入黑色 /逃跑”和“唤醒我”。</p><p>然后，他从2020年的专辑“ After Hore”中进行了一连串的热门歌曲，包括标​​题曲目，“太晚”和“逃离洛杉矶”，然后介绍了特别的嘉宾<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/playboi-carti">Playboi Carti</a>播放“ Fe！n”（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-scott">Travis Scott</a> Cover ），“直到我流血”和“永恒”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Timing - The Weeknd (Ft Playboi Carti) (Live)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/weHe8LS-yFA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>巴西艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anitta">安妮塔（Anitta</a> ）也加入了另一条未发行的曲目，被认为被称为“圣保罗”。其他未发行的曲目首次亮相是“唤醒我”，“带我回到洛杉矶”，“在火焰中跳舞”，“让我们结束一切”，“逃跑”，专辑​​的假定标题曲目“他离开了。</p><p>在其他地方，他演奏了自己的热门歌曲，包括“拯救您的眼泪”，“小于零”和“盲目的灯光”，最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknds-blinding-lights-becomes-first-song-ever-to-hit-four-billion-streams-on-spotify-3570777">成为历史上第一首在Spotify上吸引40亿溪流的歌曲</a>，现在是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknds-blinding-lights-becomes-spotifys-most-streamed-song-of-all-time-3372843">Spotify的所有歌曲中最流行的歌曲时间</a>。</p><p>查看完整的列表，并观看下面的整个表演。</p><h3> <strong>Weeknd的圣保罗集体清单是：</strong></h3><p> <strong>“人群”<br /></strong> <strong>“淡入黑色 /逃跑”（未发行的歌）</strong><br /> <strong>“叫醒我”（未发行的歌）</strong><br /> <strong>“下班后”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;为时已晚&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“屏住呼吸”</strong><br /><strong>牺牲（瑞典房屋黑手党混音）</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;我如何让你爱我？</strong><br /> <strong>“逃离洛杉矶”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;带我回到洛杉矶（未发行的歌）</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;在火焰中跳舞（未发行的歌）</strong><br /> <strong>“直到我流血”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;fe！</strong><br /> <strong>“直到我流血”（与Playboi Carti一起出来）</strong><br /> <strong>“永恒”（带Playboi Carti的Playboi Carti封面）</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;圣保罗（与安妮塔（Anitta），未发行的歌曲）</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;狠心&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“在我之后重复”（插曲）</strong><br /> <strong>“让我们结束一切”（未发行的歌）</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;信仰&#39;</strong><br /><strong>又一个人&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“逃跑”（未发行的歌）</strong><br /> <strong>“过时”</strong><br /> <strong>“还有其他人吗？”</strong><br /> <strong>“最难爱”</strong><br /> <strong>“害怕活着”</strong><br /> <strong>“拯救你的眼泪”</strong><br /> <strong>“小于零”</strong><br /> <strong>“盲灯”</strong><br /> <strong>“明天快点”（未发行的歌）</strong> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="周末 - 圣保罗直播" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/A4WgT0QOXhs?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这部三部曲的最后一部分将标志着自2022年的“ Dawn FM”以来的《周末》的第一张专辑。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463"><em>NME</em>在四星级的评论中写道</a>：“&#39;Dawn FM&#39;感觉就像是Weeknd与自己和平的旅程的第一步；也许下次我们收到他的来信时，他将充分拥抱一天的光芒。”</p><p>在其他新闻中，据报道，今年早些时候，《周末》巨大的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknds-blinding-lights-becomes-first-song-ever-to-hit-four-billion-streams-on-spotify-3570777">“盲目灯”已成为历史上第一首在Spotify上吸引40亿溪流的歌曲</a>。该曲目在2019年底发行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-after-hours-review-his-most-all-encompassing-record-to-date-is-also-an-existential-quandary-2632591">“后小时”</a>专辑中被称为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknds-blinding-lights-becomes-spotifys-most-streamed-song-of-all-time-3372843">Spotify最流行的歌曲</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-the-weeknd-played-at-his-special-sao-paulo-concert-3791657">这是Weeknd在他的特别圣保罗音乐会上演奏的帖子，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
